name: Mayasuran Navy Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the more common ship hulls, weapons, and fighter LPCs from the Mayasuran Navy.

name: Mayasuran Navy Warship Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the heavier warships from the Mayasuran Navy.

name: Mayasuran Navy Capital Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the capitals from from the Mayasuran Navy.

name: Mayasuran Prime Warship Blueprint Package
desc: A set of blueprints that enable heavy industry to produce the near-legendary hulls employed by the Mayasuran Navy. The continued existence - and location - of these blueprints is forever lost to the annals of time.

name: Mayasuran Navy Weapon Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the weapon LPCs from the Mayasuran Navy.
